{"tid":870301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MK餐廳追數爆激戰 護花南亞男一打10 勇鬥10名本地男","createTime":"2018-10-21T04:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T06:49:48.000Z","uid":2748,"like":157,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"377bacc83a4fa703e6ef15646d310a64bd3e22e3","tid":870301,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:21:45.000Z","msg":"旺角上海街59號翠河餐廳，凌晨1時許，41歲持香港身份證的越南女子偕31歲持行街紙的巴基斯坦男友在店內食飯，其間約10名本地男子掩至，聲言越南女欠債未還，雙方頓起爭執，互相推撞大打出手。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，巴漢孔武有力，與女友奮力反抗，他自己上衣也被扯爛；追數男即使人多勢眾，也佔不到上風，姓高男子衝落一樓㕑房，撿起約8吋長切肉刀作武器。<br />\n警方接報持盾牌趕至，氣氛緊張，但追數男四散逃去，當場只截獲兩人，分別姓高(39歲)及姓葉(51歲)。兩人與事主情侶均涉嫌打架被捕，四人均告受傷，但拒絕送院，返警署協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181021/58817679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181021%2F58817679&d=3pzowEE%2BkIHXpw4OszZwBQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=49a9142d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181021%2F58817679&h=d452cc6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181021/58817679</a>"},{"pid":"d6faf49407e4a473de0e56480b14bdd8365363ac","tid":870301,"uid":28765,"like":495,"dislike":3,"score":492,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"屌 之前我地1打5宜家比人追返"},{"pid":"0f82552e33bef76e211b015bed7a4d2803f35d8c","tid":870301,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":41,"score":-39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"又係南亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662b67a9ef9ef15353efe4e561e086862b60c1cb","tid":870301,"uid":177089,"like":391,"dislike":1,"score":390,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"垃圾mk 10個打人1個都唔夠做 本土黑遲早俾人消滅"},{"pid":"108479ebe492030e78032da9b92cc7a096aee7fb","tid":870301,"uid":41821,"like":143,"dislike":3,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"香港以後係南世人話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港燦返祖國生活吧"},{"pid":"28c45fdd7fb53cad89525b319cd188a9d4400686","tid":870301,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6faf49407e4a473de0e56480b14bdd8365363ac","tid":870301,"uid":28765,"like":495,"dislike":3,"score":492,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"屌 之前我地1打5宜家比人追返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52342ffcccf57434d38d1a8a2440847092523c8","tid":870301,"uid":810,"like":181,"dislike":0,"score":181,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"黑社會喎<br />\n十打一都打輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecab0114dc1c7ac6ac8f3fd30ce70d2149c3eda","tid":870301,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b52342ffcccf57434d38d1a8a2440847092523c8","tid":870301,"uid":810,"like":181,"dislike":0,"score":181,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"黑社會喎<br />\n十打一都打輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e7d5243e73248e0683d1b2629b95e0b453968f","tid":870301,"uid":62760,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"冇浩南同山雞係差啲"},{"pid":"ef8cfdb2aacd91b41deb0e9065473a2a4f747262","tid":870301,"uid":26451,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01b50a72b3b2b19cb5c530ce86d7c1636ab921f8","tid":870301,"uid":2748,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:40:31.000Z","msg":"旺角茶餐廳追債爆混戰　巴籍聲請漢以一敵十<br />\n<br />\n一名31歲巴籍聲請漢，今日（21日）凌晨1時許，偕41歲越南籍女友在旺角上海街59號一間茶餐廳消夜時，突有10名本地大漢風聞而至將2人包圍，並向女子追債，有人回應已「還晒」，但大漢強指欠債未清，雙方為此爭吵，大漢恃人多勢眾向2人圍毆，巴漢僅得雙拳，仍奮力以一敵十，場面混亂，杯碟橫飛，其他食客爭相走避，大漢則未能佔得上風，其中一人在餐廳取來一柄30公分長利刀指嚇。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方接報餐廳「開大片」，派出多名警員持盾牌迅速趕至鎮壓，當場截停2名分別姓高（39歲）及姓葉（51歲）男子，其餘則已逃去。事件中，4人面及手部受傷，傷勢均輕微，俱拒絕送院治理，其中南亞漢傷及眼角，需貼上膠布敷治。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員經調查後，案件涉及的債項與高有關，已將4人一併拘捕，同涉嫌在公眾地方打架，高亦涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器。警方仍調查案件內情，並追緝其他涉案人士。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181021/photo/bkn-20181021023016881-1021_00822_001_03p.jpg?20181021095136\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181021%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181021023016881-1021_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20181021095136&h=8d0a0ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被捕南亞漢眼角受輕傷。（葉嘉文攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181021/mobile/bkn-20181021023016881-1021_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181021%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181021023016881-1021_00822_001.html&d=3pzowEE%2BkIHXpw4OszZwBQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=08d4b621\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181021/mobile/bkn-20181021023016881-1021_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4e5164c083d3cdb9568ca5b449c7bdf25f284b62","tid":870301,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946fdf38cb27beb2dd050508483d57a8f934832d","tid":870301,"uid":2748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887bb9b66e766a870c030ca1606bca56faf46dcf","tid":870301,"uid":11127,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"屌香港黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br 